Map Name:

- Zm_snow_bunker_hellz_fix

Map Information:

- Default Cubemaps
- 64 spawn points
- FPS (Hints,Skips,Areaportals,Funcoccluder)
- Several secrets (Tele's)

I took the map cs_siege in the idea of making a zombie map! There are several teleporters, hideouts solo (trucks, under a rock, in the car ...) and hideouts in cooperation (bunker under the stairs, on the letters ...)

I hope you enjoy my first map, thank you for your comment =)
